text: Maria Kihl or Mia Kihl (born April 23, 1979 in Stockholm), is a Swedish voice actress. == Filmography == *Fairly Odd Parents - Vicky (Starting from Season 2). *Goof Troop - Max. *Quack Pack - Louie. *TaleSpin - Molly Cunningham (1st Voice), Additional Voices. *Total Drama Island - Sadie. *Yu-Gi-Oh! - Anzu Mazaki *Winx Club - Flora == Other websites == * Mia Kihl at Svensk Filmdatabases Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish voice actors
